(640, 12, 369024682233724064, 971222761721757410, 150, 1.33, 199.5, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:46', '2026-05-18 04:43:32', 49.5, -98.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Atlético Madrid, currently in 4th and vying for a Champions League spot, has strong motivation to secure a positive result. Draw No Bet on Atlético provides safety, and the odds of 1.33 are reasonable for a low-risk return given their higher motivation and form versus lower-ranked Girona.', 8),
(641, 12, 278172329527356781, 1059049118248910271, 20, 1.29, 25.8, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:47', '2026-05-18 04:43:32', 5.8, -13.1, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'The \'DOUBLE_CHANCE 12\' bet offers a good balance of low risk and decent odds at 1.29, covering both teams to win. Villarreal is motivated to secure their Champions League spot and Rayo Vallecano has no strong motivation.', 12),
(642, 12, 156679327416791783, 444611341263780813, 100, 1.4, 140, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:47', '2026-05-18 04:43:32', 40, -18.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Alaves needs a result to avoid potential relegation, while Oviedo is already relegated. Alaves has motivation, making the Draw No Bet on Away a safe choice.', 11),
(643, 12, 133093590280528384, 209923074771175965, 80, 1.29, 103.2, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:47', '2026-05-18 04:43:32', 23.2, -58.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Betting on \'OVER 1.5\' goals at 1.29 odds offers a solid balance between probability and return. Both teams, Levante and Mallorca, are in a relegation battle and will likely play aggressively, seeking goals to boost survival chances.', 10),
(644, 12, 111059860609990956, 556399206970260019, 70, 1.24, 86.8, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:48', '2026-05-18 04:43:32', 16.8, -82.1, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Getafe is motivated to secure a Conference League qualification spot, while Elche has little left to play for. The \'AWAY UNDER 1.5\' bet at 1.24 offers a high chance of winning with Getafe\'s relatively weak offensive performance and Elche\'s decent defense.', 9),
(645, 12, 487430418441049859, 238144728992446783, 150, 1.26, 189, 'lost', '2026-05-17 06:33:48', '2026-05-18 04:43:29', -150, -180.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'West Ham is in a relegation zone and motivated to fight for points. Betting on Away handicap -2 at low odds of 1.26 is the safest choice given West Ham\'s need to avoid relegation, despite Newcastle\'s low motivation.', 1),
(646, 12, 429638702822663337, 879233105594296903, 100, 1.3, 130, 'lost', '2026-05-17 06:33:48', '2026-05-18 04:43:35', -100, -23.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Atalanta is in 7th place with no European or relegation pressure, but they are hosting Bologna, who are positioned 8th and also lack motivation. Among the available odds, the \'HOME\' selection with odds of 1.30 on a \'DRAW NO BET\' offers a secure low-risk option on Atalanta, capitalizing on their home advantage and recent form, without the risk of a draw outcome.', 18),
(647, 12, 821939774286057539, 555820363377099559, 30, 1.2, 36, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:49', '2026-05-18 04:43:29', 6, -174.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Betting on \'UNDER 4.5\' goals at odds of 1.2 offers a high probability as neither Brentford nor Crystal Palace have strong offensive records, and neither team has strong motivational factors at play given their mid-table standings with no European or relegation concerns.', 2),
(648, 12, 817679963507755034, 955924048614961660, 100, 2, 200, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:49', '2026-05-18 04:43:29', 100, -74.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Both Everton and Sunderland are in mid-table positions with no outcome at stake, reducing incentive for either to push for a win. Sunderland\'s defensive away game, paired with Everton\'s average form, supports a safety-first approach, making X2 (Sunderland or draw) at odds 2 a moderate-risk choice.', 3),
(649, 12, 381432335323876713, 487434819804233377, 150, 1.19, 178.5, 'lost', '2026-05-17 06:33:49', '2026-05-18 04:43:29', -150, -224.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Brighton & Hove Albion is motivated to secure a spot in the Conference League playoffs. The odds for Brighton to score over 0.5 goals (1.19) reflect their ability to find the net against Leeds, who have little to play for. It\'s a low-risk bet in this context.', 4),
(650, 12, 1077051836618116889, 29517349607613430, 50, 1.27, 63.5, 'lost', '2026-05-17 06:33:50', '2026-05-18 04:43:35', -50, -73.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Inter is leading the league and facing Verona, who are at the bottom with relegation confirmed. Inter are highly motivated to secure full points to maintain their lead and possibly win the league. Hence, betting on Inter to win at odds of 1.27 is the safest pick with a strong probability of success.', 19),
(651, 12, 64543661625821034, 198051192906302364, 50, 1.2, 60, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:50', '2026-05-18 04:43:29', 10, -214.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Manchester United is motivated to secure their Champions League spot, playing at home with stronger league form than Nottingham Forest, whose position is less urgent. Bet \'1X\' for the safer result in terms of probable home or draw outcome given current standings and incentives.', 5),
(652, 12, 1090975014214158688, 589556191464555814, 50, 1.25, 62.5, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:50', '2026-05-18 04:43:35', 12.5, -37.4, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'The DRAW NO BET on AC Milan at odds of 1.25 offers a low-risk opportunity as AC Milan is strongly motivated to win and secure a Champions League spot, being 4th in Serie A standings with Roma closely behind. Genoa, with no real outcome at stake, is less motivated. DRAW NO BET ensures the stake is returned if there\'s a draw.', 21),
(653, 12, 816283885503929978, 643152929517074290, 120, 1.2, 144, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:51', '2026-05-18 04:43:35', 24, -49.9, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Como is pushing for European qualification with a strong defensive record, making the UNDER 4.5 goals at odds of 1.20 a safe pick against a less motivated Parma.', 20),
(654, 12, 205368647959795593, 884420972964297897, 150, 1.18, 177, 'lost', '2026-05-17 06:33:51', '2026-05-18 04:43:35', -150, -187.4, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Fiorentina is in a low playoff position with no pressure, likely not scoring much. The bet on away team under 1.5 goals with odds of 1.18 offers a high probability considering Juventus\' strong defense.', 22),
(655, 12, 115837359779618786, 1050180632833764097, 30, 1.22, 36.6, 'won', '2026-05-17 06:33:51', '2026-05-18 04:43:35', 6.6, -180.8, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Roma has a strong motivation for a positive result to secure Europa League qualification, making Double Chance 12 (either team wins) at 1.22 a logical and safe pick given the competitive context.', 23),
(656, 11, 594789860760193405, 718574950573194845, 500, 1.26, 630, 'lost', '2026-05-17 07:54:49', '2026-05-18 04:43:38', -500, -997, NULL, NULL, 2),
(657, 11, 205368647959795593, 541215830273355827, 400, 1.34, 536, 'lost', '2026-05-17 07:58:07', '2026-05-18 04:43:35', -400, -497, NULL, NULL, 1);
INSERT INTO `user_bets` (`id`, `user_id`, `event_id`, `odd_id`, `stake`, `odds_at_bet`, `potential_return`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `real_return`, `wallet_total_result`, `prediction_type`, `explanation`, `resolved_order`) VALUES
(658, 21, 655873932854937505, 114979529104871149, 50, 3.25, 162.5, 'lost', '2026-05-18 13:23:20', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', -50, 125, 'GPT_MANUAL_UPSET_PER_TOURNAMENT', 'Potential upset-style bet: over 4.5 total goals at 3.25. Instead of backing Burnley to upset the result, this targets an aggressive game script: Arsenal pushing hard for the title, Burnley’s weak defence, and the possibility that Burnley play loosely with relegation effectively settled. It needs a high-scoring match, so confidence is moderate-low, but the odds fit the 3 to 5 upset range.', 5),
(659, 19, 655873932854937505, 1119438197071782531, 100, 1.91, 191, 'lost', '2026-05-18 13:23:20', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', -100, -333, 'GPT_MANUAL_BEST_PER_TOURNAMENT', 'Best bet: Arsenal -2 handicap at 1.91. This sits in the preferred 1.5 to 3 range and gives better value than the very short Arsenal win. Arsenal have elite table strength, +42 goal difference and title pressure to attack, while Burnley have the league’s worst defensive profile among the bottom sides. A 3+ goal Arsenal win is realistic, though the margin requirement adds risk.', 5),
(660, 17, 655873932854937505, 1006591630142086253, 100, 1.35, 135, 'lost', '2026-05-18 13:23:20', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', -100, -111, 'GPT_MANUAL_SAFEST_PER_TOURNAMENT', 'Safest eligible bet: Arsenal -1 handicap at 1.35. Arsenal are 1st with 79 points, only 2 ahead of Manchester City with 2 matches left, so they have maximum title motivation and need the win. Burnley are 19th with 21 points, -36 goal difference and 73 goals conceded, effectively already relegated because West Ham are 15 points ahead with only 6 potential points left for Burnley. Arsenal should win clearly.', 5),
(661, 9, 655873932854937505, 92355302200545365, 20, 3.1, 62, 'lost', '2026-05-18 13:23:22', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', -20, -42.8, 'GPT_MANUAL_DAILY_UPSET', 'Reconsidered potential upset bet: Arsenal -3 handicap at 3.10. This is not an upset against Arsenal, but it is an upset-style aggressive margin bet within the requested odds range of 3 to 5. Arsenal are in a must-win title race, Burnley are effectively relegated with -36 goal difference and 73 conceded, so a heavy Arsenal win is more realistic than Burnley avoiding defeat. Main risk: Arsenal win comfortably but only by 2 or 3 goals depending on handicap settlement.', 2),
(662, 5, 655873932854937505, 1119438197071782531, 20, 1.91, 38.2, 'lost', '2026-05-18 13:23:22', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', -20, -71.85, 'GPT_MANUAL_DAILY_BEST', 'Best bet: Arsenal -2 handicap at 1.91. The price is much better than the simple Arsenal win markets, while still fitting the standings story: Arsenal need a strong home win for the title race and have +42 goal difference; Burnley have one of the weakest defensive records in the league and almost no survival motivation left. A 3-goal Arsenal win is plausible, though the extra margin requirement makes it riskier than -1.', 2),
(663, 6, 655873932854937505, 1006591630142086253, 30, 1.35, 40.5, 'lost', '2026-05-18 13:23:22', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', -30, 49.2, 'GPT_MANUAL_DAILY_SAFEST', 'Safest eligible bet: Arsenal -1 handicap at 1.35. Arsenal are 1st with 79 points, only 2 ahead of Manchester City with 2 games left, so this is a must-win title-race match. Burnley are 19th with 21 points, -36 goal difference, 73 goals conceded, and are effectively already relegated because West Ham are 15 points ahead with only 6 points available to Burnley. Arsenal motivation and class are both much higher, and a win by 2+ is strongly supported by the table gap.', 2),
(664, 8, 655873932854937505, 1136975104456599031, 50, 2.9, 145, 'won', '2026-05-18 13:23:44', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', 95, 504.3, 'GET_ONE_BEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Arsenal has high motivation to secure the title, likely playing aggressively against a weak Burnley defense. The implied probability of UNDER 2.5 goals at 2.9 odds suggests a strong value, given Arsenal\'s defensive strength and Burnley\'s struggle to score, especially with their limited attacking edge against top teams.', 31),
(665, 13, 655873932854937505, 870974107829245043, 20, 7.6, 152, 'lost', '2026-05-18 13:24:09', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', -20, -172.4, 'GET_ONE_UPSET_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Burnley is a relegation-threatened team with two games remaining, and they are desperate for points. Arsenal, while leading, may feel some pressure but also could be complacent due to their current position. The odds on Burnley to win or draw offer significant value considering the high stakes for Burnley and potential Arsenal pressure or squad rotation.', 44),
(666, 12, 655873932854937505, 783750715576514042, 150, 1.11, 166.5, 'won', '2026-05-18 13:24:09', '2026-05-19 05:38:10', 16.5, -427.2, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Arsenal is leading the league and playing at home with strong motivation to secure the title against a low-performing Burnley, making \'Home Win\' at 1.11 a very safe bet.', 32),
(667, 21, 720209503409981288, 651706047858847571, 50, 3.87, 193.5, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:00:38', '2026-05-19 13:00:38', 0, 0, 'GPT_MANUAL_UPSET_PER_TOURNAMENT', 'Chelsea vs Tottenham draw at 3.87 is the most attractive upset-style outcome. Chelsea are more motivated due to a possible late push toward European qualification, but they have been inconsistent all season with a perfectly balanced 13-10-13 record. Tottenham sit 17th and have little table pressure, which can sometimes make them dangerous and more open in derby matches. Both teams concede regularly and neither has shown elite control this season. A tense, chaotic London derby ending level is realistic at strong odds.', 0),
(668, 19, 826886104499883895, 894482512603869930, 100, 1.5, 150, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:00:38', '2026-05-19 13:00:38', 0, 0, 'GPT_MANUAL_BEST_PER_TOURNAMENT', 'Bournemouth vs Manchester City — BTTS YES at 1.5 stands out as the best balance of value and probability. Bournemouth are highly motivated to secure European football and cannot sit back defensively, especially at home. They have scored 56 goals this season and face a City side that will aggressively push for victory because of the title race. Manchester City average elite attacking numbers with 75 goals scored, while Bournemouth have conceded 52. Both teams have strong reasons to attack, making goals at both ends very likely.', 0),
(669, 17, 826886104499883895, 300737756271875725, 100, 1.22, 122, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:00:38', '2026-05-19 13:00:38', 0, 0, 'GPT_MANUAL_SAFEST_PER_TOURNAMENT', 'Manchester City X2 (double chance) away to Bournemouth is the safest qualifying option above 1.20. City are still fully alive in the title race with 77 points and two matches remaining, meaning they effectively must avoid defeat to continue chasing Arsenal on 82 points. Bournemouth are motivated because they sit 6th with Europa League qualification pressure from Brighton, Brentford and Chelsea behind them, but City\'s superior quality is clear: 75 goals scored, only 5 losses all season, and a +43 goal difference. Even with Bournemouth fighting hard at home, City avoiding defeat is highly probable.', 0),
(670, 9, 720209503409981288, 762074051441914266, 30, 3.7, 111, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:00:39', '2026-05-19 13:00:39', 0, 0, 'GPT_MANUAL_DAILY_UPSET', 'Tottenham away win at Chelsea around 3.7 is the most interesting upset angle. Chelsea are more motivated because they still have an outside European push with two matches left, but they remain inconsistent all season at 13 wins, 10 draws and 13 losses. Tottenham are low in the table yet still possess enough attacking quality to hurt Chelsea in an open derby game. London derbies are historically volatile, and Spurs still have enough offensive talent to exploit Chelsea\'s defensive instability despite weaker overall league performance.', 0),
(671, 5, 826886104499883895, 894482512603869930, 30, 1.5, 45, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:00:39', '2026-05-19 13:00:39', 0, 0, 'GPT_MANUAL_DAILY_BEST', 'Bournemouth vs Manchester City — Both Teams To Score YES at 1.5 is the strongest value bet in the preferred range. Bournemouth are chasing European qualification and cannot simply defend; they average strong attacking production with 56 goals scored. Manchester City need victory for the title chase and average over two goals per game. Bournemouth have conceded 52 goals, while City have scored 75, so City should create many chances. At the same time Bournemouth\'s home motivation and attacking urgency make a home goal very realistic.', 0),
(672, 6, 826886104499883895, 300737756271875725, 40, 1.22, 48.8, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:00:39', '2026-05-19 13:00:39', 0, 0, 'GPT_MANUAL_DAILY_SAFEST', 'Manchester City X2 (double chance) away at Bournemouth looks like the safest available option above 1.20. City are still in the title race with 77 points and two games remaining, meaning every match is effectively must-win to pressure Arsenal on 82 points. Bournemouth are motivated for Europa League qualification at 55 points, but City possess vastly superior squad quality, scoring power (75 goals vs 56), and equal +43 goal difference despite facing stronger pressure all season. The market price of 1.22 reflects City being highly unlikely to lose even away from home.', 0),
(673, 13, 720209503409981288, 203867391954698923, 50, 2.62, 131, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:03:23', '2026-05-19 13:03:23', 0, 0, 'GET_ONE_UPSET_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Tottenham is facing relegation threat with remaining games and potential points to stay safe, while Chelsea has no outcome pressure. As these teams meet, Spurs will be highly motivated for a result, making the Draw No Bet for Tottenham at odds of 2.62 a plausible upset with calculated risk.', 0),
(674, 13, 826886104499883895, 1131652762651938937, 20, 4.55, 91, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:03:23', '2026-05-19 13:03:23', 0, 0, 'GET_ONE_UPSET_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'AFC Bournemouth, in position to secure a Europa League spot with high motivation, face Manchester City, already comfortable in Champions League qualification but distant from the title. The odds on a Bournemouth home win are high at 4.55, suggesting City may not be as focused or intense, making this a plausible upset scenario.', 0),
(675, 12, 720209503409981288, 631655239261721702, 150, 1.45, 217.5, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:03:23', '2026-05-19 13:03:23', 0, 0, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Chelsea has nothing to play for, but Tottenham is close to relegation and very motivated. A \'Draw No Bet\' on Chelsea offers good balance with decent odds for a team not facing strong incentives from Tottenham.', 0),
(676, 12, 826886104499883895, 769462643214566206, 50, 1.22, 61, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:03:25', '2026-05-19 13:03:25', 0, 0, 'GET_ONE_SAFEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Manchester City has high motivation to secure full points in the title race, and the \'AWAY\' handicap (-1) at 1.22 provides value with reasonable safety, reflecting City\'s likely push for a decisive win.', 0),
(677, 8, 720209503409981288, 762074051441914266, 30, 3.7, 111, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:03:25', '2026-05-19 13:03:25', 0, 0, 'GET_ONE_BEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Tottenham is still fighting for Premier League survival and has motivation, making the away win at 3.7 odds a strong value bet compared to implied probability, given Chelsea\'s mid-table position and lower motivation.', 0),
(678, 8, 826886104499883895, 204294329626175036, 50, 2.6, 130, 'pending', '2026-05-19 13:03:25', '2026-05-19 13:03:25', 0, 0, 'GET_ONE_BEST_FOR_EVENT_DEFAULT', 'Manchester City is highly motivated to win as they are still in contention for the Premier League title. The handicap line of Manchester City -1 offers value at 2.6 odds, as they are in strong form and need a result to pressure Arsenal. With two games remaining and a strong squad, City can cover this handicap against a mid-table Bournemouth, whose motivation for Europa League is less pressing.', 0);
